messages.message: Hi team, do we have plans to add a custom time range option to the deployment metrics dashboard vs the current 6 hours, 24 hours, 7 days and 30 days options? RSA asked about this in the AI Hub Advancement webinar

Hey @leila.tan - nothing prioritized in the short-term, but we have this initiative in the backlog to support storing these metrics beyond 30 days: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-2404

Any details on the time groupings and time periods they'd ideally want to use?
